{"tid":1805918,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【低風險行動】【和理非】落街前，麻煩印文宣","createTime":"2020-01-01T02:59:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-01T03:45:57.000Z","uid":253691,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e75d0eaf92bc507eaa9fd04a528849b1610b8812","tid":1805918,"uid":253691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T02:59:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">tl;dr</span></span>：每人印 2 張文宣圖，帶出街，1 張自己貼，1 張邀請同路人貼（當然文宣嘅野，多多益善<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n每次嘅遊行，集會，除左集氣，製造人多畫面之外，重有一樣野可以做，就係重建連儂牆。<span style=\"color: red;\">只要有人，周圍都可以係連儂牆</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">一：人多好辦事</span></span><br />\n幾個月前，大家已經開發「秒貼文宣」技能，粗略計算，<span style=\"color: red;\">用流水式分工，一個人負責噴，幾個人負責貼，快到仆街</span>；亦因為人多，顛狗有顧忌，亂咬機會微。<br />\n<br />\n揾唔返流水式極速貼文宣例子，用住呢個畀大家參考，一個人貼都可以 4 秒 1 張 <a href=\"https://youtu.be/XBz_JfH8jhk?t=74\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FXBz_JfH8jhk%3Ft%3D74&d=WJuKoENqNSNgO%2FFXDb0as9UqyFx8t7fe88%2BQEXu6%2F%2FM%3D&h=2745a14e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/XBz_JfH8jhk?t=74</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">二：增加和理非嘅參與程度</span></span><br />\n好多和理非出黎除左行，貨金派飯買文具，同打卡之外，係無其他 task 做。<span style=\"color: red;\">貼文宣係一個重要嘅 task，去凝聚和理非嘅動力同埋鬥心</span>，繼續反抗極權。<br />\n<br />\n老老豆豆，叫得和理非，都唔求你地出黎好似球員咁開波，或者行好前 cover 其他前線球員。但唔等於你地坐場外冷板凳 on99。<br />\n<br />\n貼文宣就等於啦啦隊咁，鼓勵己方士氣，同時道出事實，踩鳩對面班少數派：<span style=\"color: red;\">「你班少數派廢 J，睇吓我地氣勢幾強，你做乜鳩都無用，You surrendered」</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">三：文宣開花</span></span><br />\nSimple Maths，50 萬人出黎，每人貼 2 張文宣，全城就會有多 100 萬張文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2020 第一擊，<span style=\"color: red;\">文宣開花，貼佢老母</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n----<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">文宣 sources</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/lab/extradition_gallery\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Flab%2Fextradition_gallery&d=WJuKoENqNSNgO%2FFXDb0as9UqyFx8t7fe88%2BQEXu6%2F%2FM%3D&h=d15815fe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/lab/extradition_gallery</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/pg/%E6%96%87%E5%AE%A3%E6%94%B6%E9%9B%86%E8%99%95-109138200430628/photos\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpg%2F%25E6%2596%2587%25E5%25AE%25A3%25E6%2594%25B6%25E9%259B%2586%25E8%2599%2595-109138200430628%2Fphotos&d=WJuKoENqNSNgO%2FFXDb0as9UqyFx8t7fe88%2BQEXu6%2F%2FM%3D&h=dca9acf6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/pg/%E6%96%87%E5%AE%A3%E6%94%B6%E9%9B%86%E8%99%95-109138200430628/photos</a>"},{"pid":"f9d941d352478ed3aa9fd51a514ee67bded5f782","tid":1805918,"uid":28432,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T03:20:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W4qJ0GK.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW4qJ0GK.gif&h=94956dc9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a431d77d1b06f6497f446900e3183d4b01cbd3db","tid":1805918,"uid":59392,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T03:22:18.000Z","msg":"輕鬆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64a0953342fa9428e8ec0f1f09fadbec8c015e3f","tid":1805918,"uid":253691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T03:29:32.000Z","msg":"cls 正經行動 post 無人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b90d16c26e042f5f72b292e53a006fe74d9a1ed0","tid":1805918,"uid":313974,"like":0